title: RHOBH: The Straw That Broke The Camille's Back - Live from Cleveland!
description:
Part two of the "Real Housewives of Beverly Hills" reunion brings more rocks and more glass houses. Luckily we have Season One Camille to throw a spanner in the works. Check out our recap, live from Cleveland, OH!
